{
  "stem": "2533.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Why did I, after the war, register myself as-- the lawyer, Frenzel's lawyer-- register myself as Wojciszyn, and not as Feldman?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, I didn't have any papers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't have anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Who was going to believe me who I am?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Oh, I said, then maybe I didn't want to be Jewish anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that point was that he was going to tell that I wasn't Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I only became Jewish because I wanted compensation, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I wanted from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then I told the [INAUDIBLE] and the translator I couldn't speak anymore to them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I said, could she ask him, would they found a sane man during the war who wasn't Jewish who wanted to be Jewish?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] What happened to Frenzel?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After-- I don't know exactly now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll tell you the truth, I don't know if I care anymore, because everybody was called back to give me-- he was declining.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He wasn't well.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was nearly 80 years old and all that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I was-- wasn't there alone, because somebody came to-- two Dutch people, who knew they were very interested in Sobibor.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one, Jules Schelvis, he was a few hours in Sobibor, his wife, his whole family, was a Dutchman.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He's a Dutchman.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He-- they all perished in Sobibor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was so interested.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then there was another friend, Dunya Braur.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She is a writer and she wanted to write so very badly a book about Sobibor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She even could speak Russian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She even went to Russia to interview Pechersky.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She's got it all on type.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Jules wrote a book about Sobibor, not only one, a few more in all.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That is Jules Schelvis.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "S-C-H-E-L-V-Y-S, I think.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it's like that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Jules, 'yools,' Jules.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
